 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uclaudshadowflare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ClaudShadowflare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/30/02 2:31:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12207.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Fear Breaking</span><hr size=1> That... and for the love of Solusek, tell people DO NOT TRAIN THE CAMP!  STAND AND DIE!  Tell them to look away from the monitor if they can't bear to watch.<br>
