Zeg <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uevilrulz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Evilrulz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/30/02 11:04:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12207.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> fear</span><hr size=1> We usually buff a monk to the teeth and give him SoE. Have the monk run in and do a lap around the portal hill. Once he has the train from hell he says go in GC and we have everyone run in invis, and run to the corner and LOG. Once everyone has logged the monk heads to SS and /q's. Then the monk logs back on in about 5 min and imediately FD's. Once its looks clear inthe corner he gives the ok for everyone to log on.<br>
<br>
A few notes:<br>
<br>
Have the monk hug walls and watch for golems and draco. A monk with knowlegde of fear is preferred as one that doesnt know the area usually gets DT'd.<br>
<br>
When FD in fear (whether its been proven or not) mobs seem to corpse camp you while FD. If you sit FD in the corner youll be waiting hours tryin to get everything to wander away.<br>
<br>
Dont log on immediatly after /q. After such a huge train there tends to be a &quot;backwash&quot; as everything heads back to spawn point. If your on when this happens its gonna be a long day in fear. <br>
<br>
Once everyone logs on kill the 1st few pulls/aggros as fast as you can. Each kill makes that area more safe.<br>
<br>
Anyway thats how we do it, and works fine. Even if invis drops for the clerics and such theyll still make it to camp safely 99% of the time. If something is aggroed have the chanters mez and everyone still log. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uobiquon1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Obiquon1</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/30/02 11:04:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12207.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Fear Break</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Tell them to look away from the monitor if they can't bear to watch.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
